      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "MY MACHINE (3) turned in a fair 4th placed finish last time at Gunnedah over 340m (19.95). Form here at the trip sound including four wins. Ready to return to form. LARNIE'S MAGIC (2) is a sprinter who excels over the short dashes. Was fourth last time (20.10) over 350m at Grafton in a NG. Solid record here at this trip including four wins. Has a solid record from this box including two wins and a minor placing. Has ability and can measure up. ELECTRIC ASSENT (4) goes very well at the course and distance with three wins and a placing from six starts. Scored by 1.75 lengths last time (22.47) in a Grade 4/5 over 388m at this track. Looks suited here and can measure up. MY MOON SHADOW (7) won as punters' elect last time and is a major player again.",
